# Development Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .dev.vars and fill in your values
# DO NOT commit .dev.vars to git (it's in .gitignore)

# ─── Required ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Admin API Key — protects /admin/* endpoints and dashboard login
# Generate a secure random key:
#   openssl rand -hex 32
X-API-KEY=your-secret-admin-api-key-here

# ─── Optional ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Webhook URL for anomaly alerts (Slack/Teams/custom)
# Fires when high-risk geo/identity anomalies appear
# ALERT_WEBHOOK_URL=https://hooks.slack.com/services/your/webhook/url

# Origin URL for forwarding validated requests with fraud headers
# Only needed if using markov-mail as a reverse proxy/middleware
# ORIGIN_URL=https://your-origin-service.com/api/validate

# Cloudflare API credentials (only needed for disposable domain updates via API)
# CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=your-account-id
# CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=your-api-token
